Program: Omnibus
Title: Jane's Publishing Company
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jx2
Last Broadcast Date: 16 August 1990
A history of Jane's Publishing company, producer of 'Jane's Fighting Ships'. Their publications are globally regarded as the main information reference point for every army and navy in the world. Includes interview with Managing Director Michael Goldsmith and military expert Paul Beaver.